# Docker Rules

## Structure
- docker-compose.yml at monorepo root
- client/Dockerfile for frontend
- server/Dockerfile for backend
- .env at monorepo root passed into both containers

## Services
- frontend: port 5173
- backend: port 8000
- Both must have health checks

## Rules
- Never hardcode secrets in Dockerfiles
- Use multi-stage builds for smaller images
- Use .dockerignore in both client/ and server/
- One command to run everything: docker compose up --build